Package: falconfs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-requests, python3-psycopg2, python3-kazoo, libboost-thread-dev, libboost-system-dev
Conflicts: falconfs-release
Replaces: falconfs-release
Description: FalconFS full package
 FalconFS is a high-performance distributed file system.
 This package installs the full FalconFS layout under /usr/local/falconfs,
 including deploy scripts, client binaries, regress tooling, and runtime assets.
 .
 Third-party components expected by FalconFS (for example /usr/local/pgsql,
 brpc, and prometheus-cpp) are prepared outside this package.

Package: falconfs-release
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-requests, python3-psycopg2, python3-kazoo, libboost-thread-dev, libboost-system-dev
Conflicts: falconfs
Replaces: falconfs
Provides: falconfs-runtime
Description: FalconFS release runtime package
 FalconFS release package with runtime-focused components under
 /usr/local/falconfs:
 falcon_meta, falcon_cm, falcon_cn, and falcon_dn.
 .
 This package is intended for release/runtime deployment verification and
 omits client/deploy/regress/private test assets.
